      <textAnnotation id="sid-76AAC8FA-7BC5-484D-B0E1-2C0D2874938B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Cash settlement – Actual movement of funds between bank accounts enabled via F110 run, APM, Payment batching and SAP MBC to send the payment files to the IC Vendor

For Control Countries (e.g., India, China, Vietnam) Mandatory for CASH Settlement
For Non-Control Countries: Company Codes which do not have inhouse bank relationship
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
